Zaporizhzhya district No. 188 (Post-Postup, 11 April). 

Mykhaylo Horyn (chairman of URP) lost in first round to UKRP head 
Stepan Khmara in Lviv district No. 261 (Za Vilnu Ukrainu, 30 
March). 

Mykola Horyn (chairman of Lviv Oblast Soviet), Rukh candidate, 
lost in a runoff in Lviv district No. 275 (Post-Postup, 11 
April). 

Ihor Hryniv (Supreme Soviet member) New Wave candidate, lost in 
Lviv district No. 276 (Post-Postup, 28 March). 

